title: Mediafour MacDrive v7.2.6 SFX Setup (by ToXiC)
description:
Mediafour MacDrive v7.2.6 SFX Setup (by ToXiC)

Install MacDrive 7 with one easy to use installer.

This SFX installer will:

- Install MacDrive v7.0.10
- Activate MacDrive v7.0.10 with Keygen (by Paradox)
- Update MacDrive to v7.2.6

It will also clean out old registry keys if you have had
MacDrive installed before.

Tested on Vista x32 and x64!

ENJOI.
